&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We’re excited about you because…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- 3–6 years of transfer pricing experience&lt;br&gt;- Strong knowledge of OECD, IRC 482, UK TIOPA, Finnish TP&lt;br&gt;- Experience with benchmarking databases&lt;br&gt;- Strong Excel/data analysis skills&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About DoorDash&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
