&lt;li&gt;3-4 years of experience in Workday integration development and support, including at least 1 year of experience with Workday Extend.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrable knowledge of Workday technologies such as Workday Studio, EIBs, Core Connectors, BIRT Reporting, PECI, Cloud Connectors, and Document Transformation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in data transformation languages including XSLT and XTT/ETV.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong capability in designing complex reports
